2. Identify as `%exposes-sections` all SectionBlocks named "Exposes" in `%contents`.
3. If length of `%exposes-sections` greater than 1:
   1. Prepare a `%breach` record with:
      - `filename` set to `%source`.
      - `line` set to the line number of the second `%exposes-sections`.
      - `rule-id` set to `module:structure:single-exposes`.
      - `description` set to "Multiple {length of `%exposes-sections`} Exposes sections".
   2. Append `%breach` to `%breaches`.
